"{\"uid\": \"express.co.uk-sport-tennis-1929130-Rafael-Nadal-Novak-Djokovic-Olympics-2024\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"  Rafael Nadalhas shed light on his body struggles after reaching the second round of the men's singles event at the Olympics.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 126, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Spaniard battled formore than two-and-a-half hours to beat Marton Fucsovics 6-1 4-6 6-4.\", \"from\": 127, \"to\": 219, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 127, \"end\": 139, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Spaniard_(film)\", \"score\": 0.7999966551257347, \"rank\": 0.2500000000000275, \"text\": \"The Spaniard\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q11424\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Spaniard_(film)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Spaniard_(film)\"}, {\"begin\": 190, \"end\": 206, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/M\\u00e1rton_Fucsovics\", \"score\": 0.9999999956035026, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Marton Fucsovics\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/M\\u00e1rton_Fucsovics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/M\\u00e1rton_Fucsovics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He has been rewarded with a mouthwatering showdown with his long-time rivalNovak Djokovic.\", \"from\": 221, \"to\": 311, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 302, \"end\": 310, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\", \"score\": 0.9999999996780389, \"rank\": 3.221656922394266e-10, \"text\": \"Djokovic\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It will be their 60th meeting and comes more than two years after they last faced off in the 2022 French Open quarter-final.\", \"from\": 312, \"to\": 436, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Nadal was emotional as he reflected on his victory on Court Philippe-Chatrier - the most important stage in his career - and previewed his clash with Djokovic.\", \"from\": 438, \"to\": 597, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 438, \"end\": 443, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 6.464200447762981e-13, \"text\": \"Nadal\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\"}, {\"begin\": 588, \"end\": 596, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\", \"score\": 0.9999999996780389, \"rank\": 3.221656922394266e-10, \"text\": \"Djokovic\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There were concerns that Nadal would not even play his singles match on Sunday.\", \"from\": 599, \"to\": 678, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 624, \"end\": 629, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 6.464200447762981e-13, \"text\": \"Nadal\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"His coach Carlos Moya raised fears earlier in the week after Nadal cancelled a practice session.\", \"from\": 679, \"to\": 775, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 689, \"end\": 700, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Moy\\u00e1\", \"score\": 0.9999998624716776, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Carlos Moya\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Moy\\u00e1\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Moy\\u00e1\"}, {\"begin\": 740, \"end\": 745, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 6.464200447762981e-13, \"text\": \"Nadal\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 38-year-old thenclaimed it was \\\"outrageous\\\" he was scheduled in the day sessionafter finishing a doubles match on Saturday night.\", \"from\": 776, \"to\": 909, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But he kept himself in the draw and managed to battle for three sets to beat Hungary's Fucsovics.\", \"from\": 911, \"to\": 1008, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 988, \"end\": 995, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hungary_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999612867681645, \"rank\": 3.862043393201322e-05, \"text\": \"Hungary\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hungary_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hungary_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Discussing his physical state after the match, Nadal said: \\\"Well, I am facing my body.\", \"from\": 1009, \"to\": 1095, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1056, \"end\": 1061, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 6.464200447762981e-13, \"text\": \"Nadal\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As good as I can?\", \"from\": 1096, \"to\": 1113, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's not easy, but if there is a place that you have to give it your all, then it's here.\", \"from\": 1114, \"to\": 1203, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It was a long match but at the same time, it was a good test.\", \"from\": 1205, \"to\": 1267, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The good thing is, I was able to play at a good level of tennis for a while, so that always gives me hope, and then the negative stuff is I was not able to hold that great level.\", \"from\": 1268, \"to\": 1446, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"So let us see tomorrow, another story and another kind of opponent.\\\"\", \"from\": 1447, \"to\": 1515, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Just in:Murray speaks out on great escape and explains choosing Olympics for retirement  Our community members are treated to special offers, promotions, and adverts from us and our partners.\", \"from\": 1517, \"to\": 1708, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1525, \"end\": 1531, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.9230820493072346e-40, \"text\": \"Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You can check out at any time.\", \"from\": 1709, \"to\": 1739, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Read ourPrivacy Policy    Turning his attention to his next match and his long-standing rival, Nadal continued: \\\"[We are in] different situations in our careers.\", \"from\": 1740, \"to\": 1901, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1835, \"end\": 1840, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 6.464200447762981e-13, \"text\": \"Nadal\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He's coming from being in the final of a Grand Slam, and I am coming without being very competitive in the last two years.\", \"from\": 1902, \"to\": 2024, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Let us see, it's in a special place.\", \"from\": 2025, \"to\": 2061, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I am just going to try to give my best and enjoy it as much as possible.\", \"from\": 2062, \"to\": 2134, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It has always been super special to play against Novak.\", \"from\": 2136, \"to\": 2192, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"No doubt about that, but the difference is normally we have been playing for finals or semi-finals but, this is the second round.\", \"from\": 2193, \"to\": 2322, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Of course, it's the Olympics, every match is super special playing in the Olympics.\", \"from\": 2323, \"to\": 2406, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But it's true that every single match I played against Novak, or almost every single match I played against him, I was in a different situation than I am today, so that makes it much more difficult for me.\", \"from\": 2407, \"to\": 2612, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I am more unpredictable now, but I always have hope, I always believe, and I want to give my best.\\\"\", \"from\": 2613, \"to\": 2712, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Olympics is extra special for Nadal this year as the tennis event is being played at Stade Roland Garros.\", \"from\": 2714, \"to\": 2823, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2748, \"end\": 2753, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 6.464200447762981e-13, \"text\": \"Nadal\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Spaniard has won 14 of his 22 overall Major titles at the French Open.\", \"from\": 2824, \"to\": 2898, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2824, \"end\": 2836, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Spaniard_(film)\", \"score\": 0.7999966551257347, \"rank\": 0.2500000000000275, \"text\": \"The Spaniard\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q11424\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Spaniard_(film)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Spaniard_(film)\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He lost in the first round of this year's clay-court Grand Slam but he redeemed himself by winning in the doubles withCarlos Alcarazand in the singles against Fucsovics.\", \"from\": 2899, \"to\": 3068, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Do not miss:Andy Murray delays retirement with epic Olympics comeback alongside Dan Evans  Do not miss:Draper and Evans rip into each other over Olympics living arrangements  Do not miss:Novak Djokovic responds to Andy Murray proposition at Olympic Games  We use your sign-up to provide content in ways you have consented to and to improve our understanding of you.\", \"from\": 3070, \"to\": 3435, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3082, \"end\": 3093, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.570401473734648e-61, \"text\": \"Andy Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}, {\"begin\": 3150, \"end\": 3159, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daniel_J._Evans\", \"score\": 0.894665856845261, \"rank\": 0.11773573602489382, \"text\": \"Dan Evans\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daniel_J._Evans\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daniel_J._Evans\"}, {\"begin\": 3284, \"end\": 3295, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.570401473734648e-61, \"text\": \"Andy Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This may include adverts from us and 3rd parties based on our understanding.\", \"from\": 3436, \"to\": 3512, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You can unsubscribe at any time.\", \"from\": 3513, \"to\": 3545, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Read ourPrivacy Policy    \\\"It has always been special, during all my tennis career.\", \"from\": 3546, \"to\": 3629, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Every moment that I was able to play on this court has been special by itself,\\\" he added.\", \"from\": 3630, \"to\": 3719, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Of course, I know that it's maybe the last time that I will play here.\", \"from\": 3721, \"to\": 3792, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Maybe not.\", \"from\": 3793, \"to\": 3803, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I can not confirm that because I do not know.\", \"from\": 3804, \"to\": 3849, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I really feel very loved from the French crowd and I enjoy the fact that I am able to keep playing [at] this age and have these unforgettable feelings on court, feeling the support and the love of the people.\\\"\", \"from\": 3850, \"to\": 4059, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3884, \"end\": 3890, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9674642084665076, \"rank\": 0.033371792582562496, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"SEARCH  CONNECT WITH US  TODAY'S PAPER  See today's front and back pages, download the newspaper, order back issues and use the historic Daily Express newspaper archive.\", \"from\": 4061, \"to\": 4230, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4198, \"end\": 4211, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.7182148467547114e-22, \"text\": \"Daily Express\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"EXPRESS.CO.UK  Daily Express uses notifications to keep you updated\", \"from\": 4232, \"to\": 4299, \"entities